{
  "texts": [
    "Another task that has emerged is Textual VQA, where the models must understand the text within the scene in order to generate answers.",
    "All three tasks have their own datasets [46,49,50,52,53] and have an active community developing solutions [49,84,103].",
    "Originally proposed in [49], VQA has developed beyond simple 'yes' or 'no' answers to richer natural language answers.",
    "A common thread of work is to leverage the multi-modal aspect of VQA and utilise both visual features from the input image and textual features from the question [84,85,103].One of the first works in VQA to make use of GNNs was that of Teney et al. [84].",
    "Their work is based on the clip art focused dataset [49]."
  ]
}